{"tid":258453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"海之戀無限touch】23歲魏同學：預算一千萬入市","createTime":"2017-05-26T06:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T06:41:30.000Z","uid":37675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5e957255de74b61093954f0d2bf0ee12696fe4f","tid":258453,"uid":37675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T06:41:30.000Z","msg":"由媽媽畀首期的23歲學生魏先生，今天和媽媽一齊來海之戀排隊買樓，他們排到落隊道。他表示，計劃買一個兩房單位，預算樓價800至1000萬元入市，由於仍是學生，沒有收入，層樓是媽媽支付首期及供款。他表示，現於內地廈門讀書。至於為何內地就學，他稱因自己學業成績欠佳。<span style=\"color: red;\">記者訪問魏媽媽，但阿仔話媽媽廣東話不好，所以不方便上鏡。</span><br />\n<br />\n酸都係咁話,又係一條大陸狗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170526/56744413\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170526%2F56744413&d=dYncJl1cW2%2B2jV20k7EwDiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=04b19670\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170526%2F56744413&h=0d2b74a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170526/56744413</a>"}]}